{"tid":1150633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與會者：娥特一度哽咽","createTime":"2019-05-12T04:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T05:46:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e6528af4ba0ad0ac10872cfcac7af92872429c4c","tid":1150633,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T04:04:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190512/20676509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190512%2F20676509&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNW7eFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=b4cbee78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190512%2F20676509&h=2ca0541d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190512/20676509</a><br />\n<br />\n與會者：娥特一度哽咽<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190512/large/12la6p01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190512%2Flarge%2F12la6p01.jpg&h=1634e668&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n團體昨在扶貧高峰會外諷刺官商合作扶貧無力。張志華攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】扶貧委員會高峰會今年以「創新扶貧、社商齊參與」為主題，邀請曾參與扶貧項目的商界及社福界代表到場。峰會其中一環節為兩小時閉門會議，讓獲邀人士與官員交流意見。與會者之一的香港社區組織協會幹事施麗珊會後指，特首林鄭月娥提及今年高峰會氣氛和諧，發言時更一度哽咽，「可能聯想到最近立法會啲事啦，講到想喊咁」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：指窮人數目或被高估越扶越貧 林鄭：因冇計長者資產<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多個團體杯葛<br />\n<br />\n施麗珊引述，林鄭讚揚場內無人示威鬧事，以往「撐到好行」的團體都可平靜坐低溝通，期望各個界別，日後都可以理性務實的態度與政府交流。<br />\n<br />\n其實所謂「和諧氣氛」，未必是因為無人想在峰會反對她。扶貧高峰會往年都有出席的基層團體於會場抗議，但今年多個獲邀組織都表明杯葛高峰會，包括香港社會工作者總工會、爭取低收入家庭保障聯席和同根社，昨日都參與了民陣的集會，聲援民主派於立法會法案委員會內，圖阻《逃犯條例》修訂通過。<br />\n<br />\n關注綜援低收入聯盟、撐基層墟市聯盟等多個亦未獲邀團體，他們昨早派代表在政總天橋請願，批評稱扶貧高峰會多年來，選擇性邀請參與者，約40人在政府總部場外高呼，「高官商家傾扶貧，基層政策好難行」等口號，斥責商界如願主動承擔社會責任，貧富懸殊便不會日益加劇。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁銘恩  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n指窮人數目或被高估越扶越貧 林鄭：因冇計長者資產<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\nSweet Monster軟雪糕 大腸菌群超標1.8倍"},{"pid":"8bc4fd5fa692adfb46bd11a902c46b3182d7ebab","tid":1150633,"uid":249885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T04:08:22.000Z","msg":"佢會喊？？？？"},{"pid":"1cc79b14b9f86da416f970fc8491fa9d9f721827","tid":1150633,"uid":60131,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T04:09:11.000Z","msg":"頂佢個肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己住大大間禮賓府，幾十萬人工一個月，又唔駛向納稅人交代就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2badf959d277e8e7940202f46d1eb872c29b0b","tid":1150633,"uid":29093,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"8bc4fd5fa692adfb46bd11a902c46b3182d7ebab","tid":1150633,"uid":249885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T04:08:22.000Z","msg":"佢會喊？？？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T04:10:26.000Z","msg":"賣港賣得咁成功， 係開心既"},{"pid":"779a2192483b916aba5516731dd19f2606f6415d","tid":1150633,"uid":2230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1cc79b14b9f86da416f970fc8491fa9d9f721827","tid":1150633,"uid":60131,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T04:09:11.000Z","msg":"頂佢個肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己住大大間禮賓府，幾十萬人工一個月，又唔駛向納稅人交代就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T04:12:38.000Z","msg":"40萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該官員人工要跟番國家拎萬3蚊咪算"},{"pid":"399226cb3b1dff13c06f09ec2bfeb6ad9fe21e82","tid":1150633,"uid":31237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T04:13:05.000Z","msg":"鱷魚淚"},{"pid":"59666b5c303eb6e72ab72a2e12dab983ce3871c8","tid":1150633,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T05:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /